== 制作 ==
=== 开发 ===
2004年2月，《{{le|惩罚者 (电影)|The Punisher (film)|惩罚者}}》剧院首映的两个月前，[[狮门娱乐|狮门娱乐]]宣布有意向制作续集《惩罚者2》。[[漫威影业|漫威影业]]主席兼总裁{{le|阿维·阿拉德|Avi Arad}}表示有兴趣开发惩罚者品牌，认为第二部将“成为漫威第五个成为续集作品的产品”<ref>{{cite web | first=Clint | last=Morris | url=http://www.moviehole.net/news/3292.html | title=Lions Gate starting on ''The Punisher 2'' | work=Moviehole.net | date=2004-02-27 | accessdate=2006-08-31 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050508202548/http://www.moviehole.net/news/3292.html | archivedate=2005-05-08 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月，电影前作的导演{{le|乔纳森·汉斯利|Jonathan Hensleigh}}表示有意与[[托马斯·简|托马斯·简]]在《惩罚者2》中再度合作<ref>{{cite web | author=Ken P. | url=http://filmforce.ign.com/articles/496/496784p5.html | title=An Interview with Jonathan Hensleigh | work=IGN | date=2004-03-05 | accessdate=2006-08-31 | archive-date=2012-03-16 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66CEdXVNw?url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/496/496784p5.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月，简透露第二部的反派为{{le|拼图 (漫威角色|Jigsaw (Marvel Comics)|拼图}}<ref>{{cite web | first=William | last=Keck | url=https://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2004-04-13-punisher-premiere_x.htm | title=Rebecca is quiet at 'Punisher' premiere | work=[[今日美國|USA Today]] | date=2004-04-13 | accessdate=2006-09-01 | archive-date=2012-03-16 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66CEiglV8?url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2004-04-13-punisher-premiere_x.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月，简表示，鉴于《惩罚者》DVD销量喜人，工作室有意制作续集《惩罚者2》，而该片的初步预算正制定中<ref>{{cite web | first=Jonah | last=Weiland | url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=4272 | title=Actor Thomas Jane Talks 'Bad Planet' and Other Comics Work | work=Comic Book Resources | date=2004-11-22 | accessdate=2006-08-31 | archive-date=2012-03-16 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66CEjmM3N?url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2005年3月，[[漫威影业|漫威影业]]公布《惩罚者2》将于2006年上映<ref>{{cite web | url=http://tv.ign.com/articles/594/594490p1.html | title=Marvel Movie Update | work=IGN | date=2005-03-08 | accessdate=2006-08-31 | archive-date=2012-03-16 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66CEl8BzA?url=http://tv.ign.com/articles/594/594490p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月，狮门娱乐总裁乔恩·费尔特海默（{{lang|en|Jon Feltheimer}}）在狮门娱乐2005年财年第三季度的分析师电话会议中公司将完成《惩罚者2》的开发<ref>{{cite web | url=http://forums.lionsgate.com/showthread.php?t=803 | title=LGF's 2005 Fiscal 3Q Analyst Call | work=Lionsgate Forums | date=2005-04-05 | accessdate=2006-08-31 | dead-url=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927235143/http://forums.lionsgate.com/showthread.php?t=803 | archivedate=2007-09-27 }}</ref>。早在7月，阿拉德便透露影片剧本正重写，续集将在年内开拍<ref>{{cite web | first=Clint | last=Morris | url=http://www.moviehole.net/news/5876.html | title=Arad on everything comic-to-film | work=Moviehole.net | date=2005-07-01 | accessdate=2006-08-31 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060305105838/http://www.moviehole.net/news/5876.html | archivedate=2006-03-05 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月，简表示自己为影片增重12磅，希望影片于2006年底开拍<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.scifi.com/sfw/issue430/news.html | title=Jane Beefs Up For ''Punisher 2'' | work=Sci Fi Wire | date=2005-07-18 | accessdate=2006-08-31 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060721205057/http://www.scifi.com/sfw/issue430/news.html | archivedate=2006-07-21 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2006年3月，剧组宣布影片计划于路易斯安那州拍摄<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/punishernews.php?id=3957 | title=''The Punisher 2'' to Film in Louisiana | work=Superhero Hype | date=2006-03-11 | accessdate=2006-08-31 | archive-date=2006-09-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060913104121/http://www.superherohype.com/news/punishernews.php?id=3957 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，并获得路易斯安那州州秘书颁发的境内通行证<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.sec.state.la.us/public/corp_newsletter/NewCorp_20060106.txt | title=New Domestic Filings: 12/24/05 thru 12/30/05 | work=Louisiana Secretary of State | date=2005-12-23 | accessdate=2006-08-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061008093555/http://www.sec.state.la.us/public/Corp_newsletter/NewCorp_20060106.txt | archive-date=2006-10-08 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。8月，漫威娱乐公布新片名单，《惩罚者2》名列其中，制作时间有待确定<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/google/20060807005366/en | title=Marvel Reports Q2 2006 Earnings Per Share of $0.19; Raises 2006 EPS Guidance Range to $0.50 - $0.60, Reflecting Tax Benefit and Impact of Share Repurchases | work=Business Wire | date=2006-08-07 | accessdate=2009-10-23 | archive-date=2011-06-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606043646/http://www.businesswire.com/news/google/20060807005366/en | dead-url=no }}</ref>。托马斯·简（{{lang|en|Thomas Jane}}）表示编剧的草稿已完成一半，相信拍摄将于2007年2月起步。简确认反派为最初在2004年4月宣布的{{le|拼图 (漫威角色|Jigsaw (Marvel Comics)|拼图}}。不过，简表示第一部导演乔纳森·汉斯利不会回归续集<ref>{{cite web | first=Kiel | last=Phegley | url=http://www.wizarduniverse.com/movies/other/001346919.cfm | title=Up Close with Thomas Jane | work=Wizard Entertainment | date=2006-08-17 | accessdate=2006-08-31 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060917214053/http://www.wizarduniverse.com/movies/other/001346919.cfm | archivedate=2006-09-17 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，[[2005年飓风卡特里娜|2005年飓风卡特里娜]]过后回归新奥尔良的狮门娱乐宣布《惩罚者2》将在年内开拍<ref>{{cite web | first=John | last=Horn | url=http://www.azcentral.com/arizonarepublic/preview/articles/0818neworleans0818.html | title=Take 2 - Filmmakers trickle back to Katrina-devastated New Orleans | work=The Arizona Republic | date=2006-08-18 | accessdate=2006-08-31}}</ref>。10月，简表示剧本将于几周内面世，新版本会“更黑暗、更血腥，比第一部更不友好”<ref>{{cite web | first=Shawn | last=Adler | author2=Larry Carroll | url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1542923/10112006/story.jhtml | title=Movie File: 'Harry Potter,' Brad Pitt, Jason Schwartzman & More | work=MTV | date=2006-10-12 | accessdate=2006-10-12 | archive-date=2006-10-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061027045110/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1542923/10112006/story.jhtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月，剧本被{{le|斯图尔特·比蒂|Stuart Beattie}}重写<ref>{{cite web | url=http://superherohype.com/news/punishernews.php?id=5018 | title=New Writer Boards ''The Punisher 2'' | work=Superhero Hype | date=2006-12-18 | accessdate=2006-12-18 | archive-date=2007-02-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070217002345/http://www.superherohype.com/news/punishernews.php?id=5018 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

消息指《[[盾牌_(电视剧)|盾牌]]》电视剧的编剧[[寇特·舒特|寇特·舒特]]也参与电影剧本的创作。舒特确认了消息，表示很享受续集剧本的创作，指成品会更贴近于角色<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=5485 | title=Kurt Sutter Talks ''The Punisher 2'' | work=Superhero Hype | date=2006-12-18 | accessdate=2007-04-29 | archive-date=2007-04-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070415052233/http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=5485 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在单独的采访中，托马斯·简表示新剧本已经上交，每个人都希望剧本能够起效，因为剧本决定了制作成败。他进而指出，如果一切按计划进行，拍摄将在6月或7月启动<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=5516 | title=Thomas Jane on ''The Punisher 2'' | work=Superhero Hype | date=2006-12-18 | accessdate=2007-04-29 | archive-date=2007-04-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070420051203/http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=5516 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而不久后，简致信{{le|Ain't It Cool News|Ain't It Cool News}}，表示已经离开剧组：

{{blockquote|我最不应该将几个月的时间耗在一部自打一开始我就不看好的电影上面。我一直以来都喜欢漫威的人们，希望他们能过得好。与此同时，我一直在找寻一部电影，一部和其他电影一样，会让粉丝会要求我去看的电影。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=5685 | title=Thomas Jane Pulls Out of Punisher 2 | work=Superhero Hype | date=2007-05-15 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2009-08-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090802193303/http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=5685 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/32673 | title=AICN Exclusive: Thomas Jane Dropping Out of 'Punisher 2'?!? | work=Ain't It Cool News | date=2007-05-15 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2012-08-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120806015728/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/32673 | dead-url=no }}</ref>}}

=== 执导 ===
2007年5月，导演{{le|约翰·达尔|John Dahl}}正就导演事宜进行谈判，但最终退出，指原因是剧本糟糕，缺乏预算<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.collider.com/entertainment/news/article.asp/aid/4608/tcid/1 | title=John Dahl is ''not'' directing Punisher 2 | work=Collider.com | date=2007-11-06 | accessdate=2009-09-18 | dead-url=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080915034847/http://www.collider.com/entertainment/news/article.asp/aid/4608/tcid/1 | archivedate=2008-09-15 }}</ref>。6月，消息指{{le|莱茜·亚历山大|Lexi Alexander}}将接任导演<ref>{{cite web | first=Ryan | last=McLelland | title=Punisher 2 Lands a Director | work=LatinoReview.com | date=2006-06-12 | url=http://www.latinoreview.com/news.php?id=2165 | accessdate=2007-09-12 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070808055312/http://www.latinoreview.com/news.php?id=2165 | archivedate=2007-08-08 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008年12月，在一次采访中亚历山大表示她第一次拿到《惩罚者2》便同意加入项目，但在读了MAX的成人版《惩罚者》漫画后，她改变了心意。狮门向她保证，可以改变计划的风格和观感，为主角惩罚者选一位新演员<ref name="suicidegirls.com">{{cite web | url=http://suicidegirls.com/interviews/Lexi+Alexander+on+Punisher%27s+Behind+The+Scenes+War+Zone/ | title=Lexi Alexander on Punisher's Behind the Scenes War Zone | work={{tsl|en|SuicideGirls.com||SuicideGirls.com}} | date=2008-12-05 | accessdate=2008-12-05 | dead-url=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207001513/http://suicidegirls.com/interviews/Lexi+Alexander+on+Punisher%27s+Behind+The+Scenes+War+Zone/ | archivedate=2008-12-07 }}</ref>。导演亚历山大提到了她的看法，表示她希望将影片打造成回溯80年代动作片的作品：“我问能不能这样子做，他们表示实际上我们就想这么做”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://spinoff.comicbookresources.com/2014/05/05/lexi-alexander-on-punisher-war-zone-and-changing-hollywoods-old-ways/|title=Lexi Alexander on 'Punisher: War Zone,' and Changing Hollywood's Old Ways|last=Gilchrist|first=Todd|work=Comic Book Resources|date=2014-05-05|accessdate=2015-03-21|archive-date=2015-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614004435/http://spinoff.comicbookresources.com/2014/05/05/lexi-alexander-on-punisher-war-zone-and-changing-hollywoods-old-ways/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 选角 ===
7月21日，消息指演员[[雷·史蒂文森|雷·史蒂文森]]将在续集中出演惩罚者<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latinoreview.com/news.php?id=2452 |title=Exclusive Scoop: We Know Who the New Punisher Is! |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070805184505/http://www.latinoreview.com/news.php?id=2452 |archivedate=2007-08-05 |access-date=2020-08-20 }}</ref>。影片摄制定于2007年10月在蒙特利尔展开<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=6118 | title=Lionsgate Release Confirms Punisher 2 Details | work=Superhero Hype | date=2007-08-01 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2009-09-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090923074732/http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=6118 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。拍摄前，史蒂文森阅读了已发行的每期《{{le|惩罚者：法兰克·卡索传|The Punisher: Frank Castle|惩罚者MAX}}》，并接受前[[美國海軍陸戰隊武裝偵察部隊|海军陆战队武装侦察队员]]兼电影动作指导{{le|帕特·E·约翰森|Pat E. Johnson}}的耐力、武术及武器训练<ref name="collider-interview" /><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.collider.com/entertainment/interviews/article.asp/aid/10042/tcid/1 | title=Interview: Ray Stevenson on ''Punisher: War Zone'' | work=Collider.com | date=2008-12-04 | accessdate=2009-09-18 | archive-date=2009-09-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090905015515/http://www.collider.com/entertainment/interviews/article.asp/aid/10042/tcid/1 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="auto">{{Cite video | time="Training to Become the Punisher" | title=Punisher: War Zone 2-Disc Edition | medium=DVD/Blu-ray}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.collider.com/entertainment/interviews/article.asp?aid=11258&tcid=1 | title=Ray Stevenson talks ''Punisher'' | work=Collider.com | date=2009-03-15 | accessdate=2009-09-18 | archive-date=2009-09-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090928111355/http://www.collider.com/entertainment/interviews/article.asp?aid=11258&tcid=1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月，影片暂定名《惩罚者：欢迎回来，法兰克》（{{lang|en|''The Punisher: Welcome Back Frank''}}）公布。8月28日，狮门影业公布最新暂定名为《惩罚者：战争特区》<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.justpressplay.net/movies/punisher-war-zone/news/official-sequel-title-now-punisher-war-zone.html | title=Official Sequel Title Now 'Punisher: War Zone' | work=JustPressPlay.net | date=2007-08-28 | accessdate=2007-08-28 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070926235851/http://www.justpressplay.net/movies/punisher-war-zone/news/official-sequel-title-now-punisher-war-zone.html | archivedate=2007-09-26 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月中旬，导演宣布[[達什·米霍克|達什·米霍克]]（饰警探马丁·索普）、[[科林·薩爾蒙|科林·薩爾蒙]]（饰探员保罗·布迪安斯基）和{{tsl|en|Doug Hutchison|道格·哈奇森}}（饰隆尼·宾·吉姆）加入剧组。9月25日，《[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]》指[[多米尼克·韦斯特|多米尼克·韦斯特]]将出演反派拼图，[[韋恩·奈特|韋恩·奈特]]出演惩罚者的装甲兵微芯片。[[派迪·康斯丁|派迪·康斯丁]]曾考虑出演拼图，但是他的邀约后来被撤销，转给了曾拒绝该角色的韦斯特<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=6302 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-08-20 |archive-date=2009-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090112114753/http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=6302 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[小弗雷迪·普林斯|小弗雷迪·普林斯]]曾参与该角色试镜，但没有被狮门影业接纳<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.earwolf.com/episode/punisher-war-zone/ |title=Punisher: War Zone, episode #20 of How Did This Get Made? on Earwolf |publisher=Earwolf.com |date=2011-10-03 |accessdate=2013-04-23 |archive-date=2011-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006100643/http://www.earwolf.com/episode/punisher-war-zone/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片于10月22日至12月14日在蒙特利尔拍摄<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.comics2film.com/index.php?a=story&b=29543 | title='Punisher: War Zone' Shooting Dates and Crew Details | work=Comics2Film.com | date=2007-10-20 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2007-12-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071224030741/http://www.comics2film.com/index.php?a=story&b=29543 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，主体摄影持续至12月27日<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=6638 | title=Lexi Alexander on Shooting Punisher | work=Superhero Hype | date=2007-12-29 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2009-01-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090112164013/http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=6638 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008年2月14日，[[科特·萨特|科特·萨特]]宣布演职员表仲裁裁定他将从影片中除名。他表示：“我因故从影片中划掉了我的名字。原因很明显，是因为我值得列入演职员表。我的剧本草稿只有很小一部分在拍摄剧本中得到保留。他们保留了一个重要的场景，就是罗素变成拼图的那一幕。那一幕戏很残暴。很高兴他们保留下来<ref>{{cite web | url=http://sutterink.blogspot.com/2008/02/punisher-warzone-update.html | title=Punisher: War Zone Update | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2017-10-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171029202036/http://sutterink.blogspot.com/2008/02/punisher-warzone-update.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

=== 音乐 ===
虽然影片本身是“[[票房炸弹|票房炸弹]]”原声带还是取得了可观的商业成绩，位列《[[公告牌_(杂志)|公告牌]]》杂志{{tsl|en|Top Independent Albums|最强独立专辑榜}}第23位<ref name=all>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-punisher-war-zone-mw0000801266/awards|title=The Punisher: War Zone – Original Soundtrack – Awards – AllMusic|work=AllMusic|accessdate=2020-08-20|archive-date=2016-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113034654/http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-punisher-war-zone-mw0000801266/awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

影片原创配乐由{{le|迈克尔·旺德马赫|Michael Wandmacher}}谱曲，他表示制作重点是“为惩罚者塑造明确的音乐身份。我知道我要来一点黑暗、凶狠、狂野的元素，但也不能遗忘弗兰克的人性、个人所饱受的折磨以及深深的悲伤。所以，我以既是粉丝又是作曲人的角度看待这份工作。”为了让弗兰克·卡斯特的角色看起来不那么的搬掉，旺德马赫决定加入陷阱般的终止式、强大且动态的固定音型以及缓慢上扬的弦乐重复段，模仿出一个无情的实体，就像慢慢逼近的军队营部一样<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ifmagazine.com/feature.asp?article=3111 |title=Exclusive Interview: E-Notes: Composer Michael Wandmacher puts on the skull and crossbones for 'Punisher' |author=Schweiger, Daniel (Soundtrack Editor) |date=2008-12-11 |accessdate=2009-10-23 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100102200207/http://ifmagazine.com/feature.asp?article=3111 |archivedate=2010-01-02 }}</ref>。

=== 创意冲突 ===
影片计划于2008年9月12日拍摄，但推迟到三个月后的12月5日才进行<ref name="December release">{{cite web | url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=7025 | title=Punisher Will Enter War Zone 3 Months Later | work=Superhero Hype | date=2008-04-03 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2009-01-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108102639/http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=7025 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

先导预告于2008年6月12日发行。7月25日，{{tsl|en|Ain't It Cool News|Ain't It Cool News}}的哈莉·诺里斯（{{lang|en|Harry Knowles}}）撰文指影片导演莱茜·亚历山大已被除名<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/37642 | title=The Unfortunate Reality Behind ''Punisher War Zone'' | work=Ain't It Cool News | date=2008-07-25 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2019-01-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122000003/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/37642 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。第二支先导预告于圣地亚哥国际漫画展当天公布。莱茜未出席当天的活动，引发当天出席影片主创见面会的影片询问她的名字是否从影片中除名。8月15日，“拉丁评论”网（{{lang|en|Latino Review}}）报道指狮门将影片剪辑为符合PG-13评级的版本。摄影指导史蒂夫·盖纳（{{lang|en|Steve Gainer}}）后来表示影片将会是“R”级，而莱茜仍为导演<ref>{{cite web | url=http://rawstudios.invisionzone.com/index.php?showtopic=55&st=2060&p=12150&#entry12150 | title=The Punisher: WarZone, Let's talk about the reboot | work=Raw Studios | date=2008-08-16 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2012-11-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121120220653/http://rawstudios.invisionzone.com/index.php?showtopic=55&st=2060&p=12150&#entry12150 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月3日，[[IGN|IGN]]收到狮门影业的官方声明，表示莱茜未被解雇<ref>{{cite web | url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/915/915954p1.html | title=Punisher Rated, Director Staying Put | last=Linder | first=Brian | work=IGN | date=2008-10-03 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2012-04-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120416223531/http://movies.ign.com/articles/915/915954p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008年12月，在接受采访时<ref name="suicidegirls.com"/>，莱茜承认与狮门发生过严重的冲突，但否认她曾被正式除名：“我的名字从未被除去，我既不希望被除名，也没有获得解雇通知书。事实上，我们可能是在就一些和其他电影相同的问题展开讨论”。尽管流言广为流传，莱茜仍表示对最终版“感到非常开心”：

{{blockquote|我想说，这是有代价的，但我的确保持了想在银幕上放映的电影。就我个人而言，在我看来，就为了我自己的职业生涯，为了在我的承诺上加入电影的演员所作承诺而作出妥协，是非常危险的举动。我不关心这场激烈的斗争，我只想说我对银幕上的东西感到欣慰<ref name="suicidegirls.com"/>}}

2015年，莱茜对狮门影业控制影片所导致的最终版质量感到遗憾：

{{blockquote|漫威是平等的合作伙伴，但不幸的是，当存在创造性的决策冲突时，漫威将让狮门打破僵局。我一直对以这种方式打造漫威电影感到遗憾，因为漫威99%的想法都比其他制片方都要好，我也很喜欢他们。}}

莱茜表示自己没有影片最终版<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/lexi-alexander-says-she-wishes-marvel-had-made-creative-decisions-on-punisher-war-zone-instead-of-lionsgate-20150320|title=Lexi Alexander Says She Wishes Marvel Had Made Creative Decisions On 'Punisher: War Zone' Instead Of Lionsgate|last=Jagernauth|first=Kevin|work=The Playlist|date=2015-03-20|accessdate=2015-03-21|archive-date=2015-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150322225255/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/lexi-alexander-says-she-wishes-marvel-had-made-creative-decisions-on-punisher-war-zone-instead-of-lionsgate-20150320|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 发行 ==
=== 票房 ===
影片上映首周于北美2508家影院放映，收益4,271,451美元，场均1,703美元，位列票房榜第8位<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekend&id=punisher2.htm | title=Weekend Box Office for Punisher: War Zone | work=Box Office Mojo | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2012-03-16 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66CEqKm4g?url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekend | dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片国内总票房8,050,977美元，成为票房成绩最低的[[漫威漫画|漫威漫画]]改编电影，仅次于《[[黑天使_ELEKTRA|黑天使 ELEKTRA]]》和《[[霍华鸭_(电影)|霍华鸭]]》<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=marvelcomics.htm | title=Marvel Comics movies | work=Box Office Mojo | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2016-03-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302025723/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=marvelcomics.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。海外票房2,049,059美元，全球总计10,100,036美元，无法收回3500万美元的成本，沦为[[票房炸弹|票房炸弹]]<ref name="bomojo"/>。

=== 专业评价 ===
影片在[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]获得107条评论，腐烂度29%，平均得分4.28/10。网站共识写道：“《战争特区》令人回想起非常暴力、对白挑衅人的1980年代动作片演员，巧合的是这种感觉已经过时20年了”<ref name=rotten>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/punisher_war_zone/ | title=Punisher: War Zone (2008) | work=Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2008-11-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081106151737/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/punisher_war_zone/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的[[罗杰·伊伯特|罗杰·伊伯特]]打出2/4星，认为：“你已经习惯了制作粗糙的可怕电影。现在刷新你认知的作品来了。《惩罚者：战争特区》是我看过劣质的电影。”他认为电影唯一的缺陷就是“令人恶心”<ref>{{cite web | first=Roger | last=Ebert | date=2008-12-03 | title=Punisher: War Zone Review | url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20081203/REVIEWS/812039989 | work=[[芝加哥太陽報|Chicago Sun-Times]] | accessdate=2009-10-23 | archive-date=2009-03-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090325174932/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20081203%2FREVIEWS%2F812039989 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的克拉克·柯里斯（Clark Collis）认为[[雷·史蒂文森|雷·史蒂文森]]的角色应该改名叫“不太爱学习的弯曲仪”（Not-Much-of-a-Learning Curveinator）<ref>{{Cite journal | first=Clark | last=Collis | title=Review of ''Punisher: War Zone'' | journal=[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | issue=1025 | date=2008-12-12 | page=52}}</ref>。RobotBoombox.com的弗兰克·达斯塔（Frank Dasta）打出0/5星的低分：“愿上帝怜悯这部电影的灵魂！《惩罚者：战争特区》平淡无奇，完全没有原版的点，拍这部电影的人好像没有真的读过一本《惩罚者》漫画<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.robotboombox.com/audio/riffs/warzone.html | title=Robot Boombox Riffs: Punisher - War Zone | work=Robot Boombox | date=2012-11-22 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2016-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205859/http://www.robotboombox.com/audio/riffs/warzone.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

英国《[[星期日泰晤士报|星期日泰晤士报]]》的爱德华·波特（Edward Porter）打出3/5星评价，认为“尽管因为暴力内容获得18评级，影片的其他内容非常适合孩子，例如激烈的枪战、狂吠吓人的恶棍、笨拙的搭档等等，这种胡编乱造很让人享受”<ref>{{Cite news | first=Edward | last=Porter | date=2009-02-08 | title=Punisher: Warzone | url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/film_reviews/article5669742.ece | work=The Sunday Times | quote=Highly enjoyable tosh. | accessdate=2009-11-17 | archive-date=2009-03-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318114942/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/film_reviews/article5669742.ece | dead-url=no }} {{Rating|3|5}}</ref>。《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》电影记者彼得·哈特劳布（Peter Hartlaub）认为影片是“有史以来最出色的《惩罚者》电影，动作场面令人满意，黑暗故事接近于原版漫威漫画的基调<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2008/12/05/DDOH14GTQO.DTL&hw=Punisher+War+Zone&sn=002&sc=434 | title=Movie review: 'Punisher: War Zone' bloody good | work=San Francisco Chronicle | date=2008-12-05 | accessdate=2020-10-10 | archive-date=2009-02-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211013938/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2008%2F12%2F05%2FDDOH14GTQO.DTL | dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

喜剧演员{{tsl|en|Patton Oswalt|巴顿·奥斯瓦尔特}}自发行之日便公开支持这部影片，是他“今年看过最好的影片”<ref>{{cite web | first=Patton | last=Oswalt | date=2008-12-16 | title=THE "IS THIS HAPPENING?" MOVIE CLUB | url=http://pattonoswalt.com/index.cfm?page=spew&id=90 | work=PattonOswalt.com | accessdate=2011-10-05 | archive-date=2011-11-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111101104130/http://pattonoswalt.com/index.cfm?page=spew&id=90 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年10月，奥斯瓦尔特与导演莱茜在洛杉矶举行影片放映会，两人还在{{tsl|en|Paul Scheer|保罗·舍尔}}播客节目《{{tsl|en|How Did This Get Made?|这是怎么做的？}}》第20集中讨论了影片<ref>{{cite web | first=Paul | last=Scheer | date=2011-10-03 | title=Punisher: War Zone, episode #20 of How Did This Get Made? | url=http://www.earwolf.com/episode/punisher-war-zone/ | work=Earwolf | accessdate=2011-10-05 | archive-date=2011-10-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006100643/http://www.earwolf.com/episode/punisher-war-zone/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

